{"translation-revision-date":"2025-02-04T15:33:29+00:00","generator":"WP-CLI\/2.12.0","source":"admin-core\/assets\/build\/onboarding-app.js","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","lang":"en","plural-forms":"nplurals=2; plural=(n != 1);"},"Spectra":["Spectres"],"Elementor":["Elementor"],"Bricks":["Briques"],"Other":["Autre"],"Email address":["Adresse e-mail"],"Reset":["R\u00e9initialiser"],"Processing":["Traitement"],"Access all of our pro templates when you upgrade your plan to CartFlows Pro today.":["Acc\u00e9dez \u00e0 tous nos mod\u00e8les professionnels lorsque vous passez \u00e0 CartFlows Pro aujourd'hui."],"Get CartFlows Pro":["Obtenez CartFlows Pro"],"Back":["Retour"],"Importing..":["Importation.."],"Active":["Actif"],"Let's Start":["Commen\u00e7ons"],"Welcome to CartFlows":["Bienvenue chez CartFlows"],"You're only minutes away from having a more profitable WooCommerce store! This short setup wizard will help you get started with CartFlows.":["Vous \u00eates \u00e0 quelques minutes d'avoir une boutique WooCommerce plus rentable ! Ce court assistant de configuration vous aidera \u00e0 d\u00e9marrer avec CartFlows."],"Save & Continue":["Enregistrer et continuer"],"Saving":["Enregistrement"],"Hi there! Tell us which page builder you use.":["Salut ! Dites-nous quel constructeur de page vous utilisez."],"Install & Activate":["Installer et activer"],"Installing Required Plugins":["Installation des plugins requis"],"Since CartFlows uses WooCommerce, we'll set it up for you along with Cart Abandonment and Stripe Payments so you can recover abandoned orders and easily accept payments.":["\u00c9tant donn\u00e9 que CartFlows utilise WooCommerce, nous allons le configurer pour vous avec l'abandon de panier et les paiements Stripe afin que vous puissiez r\u00e9cup\u00e9rer les commandes abandonn\u00e9es et accepter facilement les paiements."],"Continuing\u2026":["En continuant\u2026"],"Continue":["Continuer"],"First Name":["Pr\u00e9nom"],"Please enter your name":["Veuillez entrer votre nom"],"Enter Your Email":["Entrez votre e-mail"],"Please Enter Name":["Veuillez entrer le nom"],"Entered email address is not a valid email":["L'adresse e-mail saisie n'est pas une adresse e-mail valide"],"Please Enter Email ID":["Veuillez entrer l'identifiant de l'e-mail"],"Skip":["Passer"],"Select Color":["S\u00e9lectionner la couleur"],"Recommended":["Recommand\u00e9"],"Upload a Logo":["T\u00e9l\u00e9charger un logo"],"Change a Logo":["Changer un logo"],"Remove logo":["Supprimer le logo"],"Suggested Dimensions: 180x60 pixels":["Dimensions sugg\u00e9r\u00e9es : 180x60 pixels"],"Oops!!! No templates found":["Oups !!! Aucun mod\u00e8le trouv\u00e9"],"Seems like no templates are available for chosen page editor. Don't worry, you can always import the store checkout template from the CartFlows setting menu.":["Il semble qu'aucun mod\u00e8le ne soit disponible pour l'\u00e9diteur de page choisi. Ne vous inqui\u00e9tez pas, vous pouvez toujours importer le mod\u00e8le de paiement du magasin depuis le menu des param\u00e8tres de CartFlows."],"Skip to Next":["Passer au suivant"],"Now let's setup your new store checkout.":["Maintenant, configurons le paiement de votre nouveau magasin."],"Choose one of the store checkout designs below. After setup you can change the text and color or even choose an entirely new store checkout design.":["Choisissez l'un des mod\u00e8les de caisse ci-dessous. Apr\u00e8s la configuration, vous pouvez modifier le texte et la couleur ou m\u00eame choisir un tout nouveau mod\u00e8le de caisse."],"Import & Continue":["Importer et continuer"],"Processing..":["Traitement en cours.."],"Importing Failed..":["\u00c9chec de l'importation.."],"Change Primary Color":["Changer la couleur principale"],"Learn more about usage tracking":["En savoir plus sur le suivi d'utilisation"],"Documentation":[""],"Something went wrong":[""],"An unexpected error occurred while loading this section. Refreshing the page should fix the issue.":[""],"Go Back":[""],"Refresh Page":[""],"Block Builder":[""],"Beaver Builder":[""],"Exit Guided Setup":[""],"Awesome \ud83d\udc4d":[""],"Set up a high-converting checkout page in minutes":[""],"Recover abandoned orders with built-in cart abandonment":[""],"Accept payments easily with Stripe integration":[""],"Works seamlessly with your existing page builder":[""],"Boost revenue with upsells, downsells, and order bumps":[""],"CartFlows \u2014 Welcome Walkthrough":[""],"Get Started with Onboarding":[""],"CartFlows works with all page builders, so don't worry if your page builder is not in the list.":[""],"Great job! Now let's install some required plugins.":[""],"Not Installed":[""],"Previous templates":[""],"Next templates":[""],"One last step.":[""],"Let's setup email reports on how your store is doing.":[""],"Let CartFlows take the guesswork out of your checkout results. Each week your store will send you an email report with key metrics and insights. You also will receive emails from us to help your store sell more.":[""],"Help improve CartFlows by sharing non-sensitive usage data.":[""],"We don't collect any personal information\u2014just basic details like your PHP version, admin language, and which features you use.":[""],"Learn more":[""],"about what we collect and why.":[""],"High-converting checkout pages":[""],"Your store now has optimized checkout pages ready to convert visitors into customers.":[""],"Cart abandonment recovery":[""],"Automatically recover lost sales with built-in cart abandonment emails.":[""],"Revenue-boosting funnels":[""],"Upsells, downsells, and order bumps are ready to maximize your average order value.":[""],"Congratulations, You Did it! \ud83c\udf89":[""],"CartFlows is set up on your website! You're now ready to build high-converting sales funnels.":[""],"Here's What You've Unlocked:":[""],"Redirecting\u2026":[""],"Go To Dashboard":[""]}}}